## 📞 Support & Getting Help

### If You Get an Error
1. **Check Console:** Press F12 > Console
2. **Read Error:** Look for red text
3. **Check Docs:** Search in README.md
4. **Verify Setup:** All 8 files present?
5. **Check API Key:** Is it correct?
6. **Try Again:** Refresh (Ctrl+F5)

### Common Error Solutions
```
"Cannot read property 'textContent' of null"
└─ Missing HTML element (typo in ID)

"API request failed"
└─ Invalid API key or network error

"Uncaught SyntaxError"
└─ Corrupted JavaScript file

"Settings not saving"
└─ localStorage disabled
```

### Useful Links
- **API Key:** https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
- **Gemini Docs:** https://ai.google.dev
- **Google Cloud:** https://console.cloud.google.com
- **Bug Report:** Check browser console (F12)

